	tv2ccLookups	OBJECT-TYPE
	SYNTAX		Counter
	ACCESS		read-only
	STATUS		mandatory
	DESCRIPTION
			"The number of NFS Version 2 calls received
			 for the NFSPROC_LOOKUP (Look Up File Name)
			 procedure, that did not result in the
			 filesystem blocking to read from disk,
			 since the last boot."
