			with request sizes between 2K-4095 bytes."
	::= { tv3WriteStats 4 }

	tv3Write8KCalls	OBJECT-TYPE
	SYNTAX		Counter
	ACCESS		read-only
	STATUS		mandatory
	DESCRIPTION
			"The number of NFS Version 3 write calls
